{"tid":244224,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想玩場暴雪英霸都咁難","createTime":"2017-05-15T09:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T04:52:42.000Z","uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35864df6ccbb6d1f5bde2e39dd2dcf8e07faa4a7","tid":244224,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"一開Game有時就要等佢個 [請稍候]，<br />\n等咗10分鐘都係冇得準備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有準備之後，齊人等排Game都可以等5分鐘都仲未開到。<br />\n<br />\n試過一個鐘淨係排到一場，啲人排5分鐘都排唔到就走，之後又排過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果斷線，之後重新返回遊戲，都可以卡住呢個重新返回遊戲嗰介頁。<br />\n<br />\n卡住就當然熄Game重開，但係開完竟然去咗大廳 &hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁多Bug點同其他Game鬥啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲話2.0"},{"pid":"7c8ba1c2c68a51546bef5f59b40fa7651c21fa32","tid":244224,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"亞洲ser冇人架喇 其他會快d"},{"pid":"4f9f12d8a114671ad97af18f6d3a05282415981c","tid":244224,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>亞洲ser冇人架喇 其他會快d</blockquote><br />\n我想解個鬥陣任務，但係個ser好爛"},{"pid":"7bec7a9bd1a3e52e4d448d9f4233dee78fe9a148","tid":244224,"uid":18507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"無知一問...隻game有人玩既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abca03df3d18d1f980aeebb297d34a218e0a1874","tid":244224,"uid":48110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:45:30.000Z","msg":"打左成日，最長等11x秒"},{"pid":"228686a8ac6de33be379df50e72f41dd9befb8db","tid":244224,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問...隻game有人玩既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔想玩，我解鬥陣任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44aae9adcca5657531bde72c90e1e3dea961ee3","tid":244224,"uid":57762,"like":0,"disli